3.41	Pirates_of_the_Caribbean_(film)	Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl	Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl is a 2003 American adventure fantasy film based on the Pirates of the Caribbean ride at Disney theme parks. It was directed by Gore Verbinski and produced by Jerry Bruckheimer. The story follows blacksmith Will Turner and pirate Captain Jack Sparrow (Johnny Depp) as they rescue the kidnapped Elizabeth Swann (Keira Knightley) from the cursed crew of the Black Pearl, captained by Hector Barbossa (Geoffrey Rush).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0e/Pirates_of_the_Caribbean_movie.jpg/220px-Pirates_of_the_Caribbean_movie.jpg
